latestPosts.caption: Feeling incredibly thankful and privileged to walk as the showstopper at the coveted 8th edition of @rongaligoodvibes ! Representing my beloved hometown, Karbi Anglong District, on such a grand stage was truly an honor. Immense gratitude to the entire fashion event team @oneunitdiphu @juliebeypi @jyotibeypi for their unwavering support and dedication. This experience was a dream come true, and I'm so proud to showcase the beauty and culture of Karbi Anglong. Thank you for this unforgettable opportunity! #Grateful #Rongali2024 #KarbiAnglong #FashionShow #ProudMoment
